00:13:37,800 --> 00:13:40,080
 for why you may in fact be misreading this.

304
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:42,000
 You see, so often when we come to this passage,

305
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:45,760
 we start in verse six, which is a command from Paul.

306
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:46,800
 Do not be anxious.

307
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:49,320
 Hey, I know things are hard.

