00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:57,160
 He's got time on the calendar.

341
00:14:57,160 --> 00:14:58,560
 You're never bothering him.

342
00:14:58,560 --> 00:15:00,240
 He's not too busy for you.

343
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:02,200
 Like when you come to him and you pray,

344
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:04,880
 you literally are crossing heaven's threshold,

345
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:10,800
 and you get to engage with the living God.

346
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:13,560
 You get to meet in his presence.

347
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:17,320
 Prayer is the passage to that place.

348
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:19,160
 That's why Paul is echoing the words of David

349
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:20,160
 from Psalm 145.

350
00:15:20,160 --> 00:15:24,520
 Psalm 145, 18 says, "The Lord is near to all."

351
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:27,000
 To who?

352
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,880
 To everybody.

