00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:30,760
 Like non-discriminatorily.

354
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:35,080
 Like God is available to everyone who calls on him.

355
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:38,480
 To anyone that prays to him.

356
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:40,560
 To all who call on him in truth.

357
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:42,720
 God is near to you.

