00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:15,240
 When God is near,

370
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:17,280
 you realize how dominating,

371
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:20,640
 and everlasting, and transcendent he is.

372
00:16:20,640 --> 00:16:25,640
 And you also realize how infinitely small

373
00:16:25,640 --> 00:16:28,200
 and urgently expiring you are.

374
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:33,800
 This is what happens when we come close to the Lord,

375
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:35,880
 when we get near to his presence.

376
00:16:35,880 --> 00:16:37,680
 The nearer we come to him,

377
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:39,760
 the clearer he becomes to us.

378
00:16:39,760 --> 00:16:43,400
 So then why do we feel so far from him at times?

