00:17:03,760 --> 00:17:06,800
 Let me tell you what I wish I could tell myself

388
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:10,120
 in past moments like that.

389
00:17:10,120 --> 00:17:15,080
 God hasn't moved.

390
00:17:15,080 --> 00:17:22,060
 God has only and always moved in one direction,

391
00:17:22,060 --> 00:17:25,400
 and it's towards us.

392
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:28,120
 God wants to be near to us.

393
00:17:28,120 --> 00:17:31,740
 That's what the Bible is trying to tell us.

394
00:17:31,740 --> 00:17:34,200
 That's what the culmination of the person of Jesus

395
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:35,540
 is making clear.

