00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:19,420
 "Don't become so absorbed by that future possibility

411
00:18:19,420 --> 00:18:25,560
 "that you forget or you neglect God's present proximity,

412
00:18:25,560 --> 00:18:28,240
 "that he's here, he's nearby."

413
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:33,600
 In the Greek, the word that Paul uses here for anxious

