00:18:35,040 --> 00:18:38,680
 It's a word that means to divide or to tear apart.

416
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:42,080
 It's literally the idea of two opposing forces

417
00:18:42,080 --> 00:18:45,240
 pulling something apart.

