00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:49,040
 Something that was whole is now being divided into two,

419
00:18:49,040 --> 00:18:50,200
 which is a really good word picture

420
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:52,280
 because that's kind of what anxiety does to us, right?

