00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:33,080
 Anxiety is like our rocking chair.

438
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:38,080
 Like it takes an initial investment of effort

439
00:19:38,080 --> 00:19:41,520
 and as you worry, it may feel nice,

440
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:46,280
 but it is terribly unproductive

441
00:19:46,280 --> 00:19:49,360
 and it takes you nowhere that you're wishing to go.

442
00:19:49,360 --> 00:19:52,400
 This is what anxiety does to us.

443
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:54,840
 And so what does Paul say?

444
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:57,560
 Like, what are we supposed to do with that?

