00:20:54,040 --> 00:20:55,920
 but pray about all of it,

470
00:20:55,920 --> 00:21:00,000
 because we have a God, a father in heaven

471
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:02,480
 that looks after us, that takes care of us,

